TO RUN NODE FOR RUNTIME ENVIRONMENT

	npm run dev


TO INSTALL REQUIRED PACKAGES

	npm i nodemon
	npm i mysql
	npm i express
	npm i node-notifier
	npm i connect-flash

To initialize with ganache type in cmd

	truffle config
	truffle deploy

Main file is test.js
First Stop mysql/apachi server

	sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 stop
	sudo /etc/init.d/mysql stop

Start Xampp Server

	sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start

Then type npm run dev to start node server and then
	
	1. type ipfs daemon on cmd
	2. open ganache
	3. type npm run dev
			in the project directory where node modules folder is available

